NAME
    Task::Tiny - install a lightweight development environment

DESCRIPTION
    Task::Tiny may be used to install a selection of tiny Pel extensions from
    the CPAN.

  Utilities
    General utilities.

    *   Exporter::Tiny

    *   Try::Tiny

    *   Config::Tiny

  Objects
    Framework for OO programming.

    *   Class::Tiny

    *   Class::Tiny::Antlers

    *   Role::Tiny

    *   Class::Method::Modifiers

  Types
    Type constraint framework.

    *   Type::Tiny

    *   Types::Path::Tiny

  Filesys
    File system manipulation.

    *   Path::Tiny

    *   Types::Path::Tiny

  HTTP
    Web stuff.

    *   HTTP::Tiny

  JSON
    JSON stuff.

    *   JSON::Tiny

  YAML
    YAML stuff.

    *   YAML::Tiny

BUGS
    Please report any bugs to
    <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=Task-Tiny>.

SEE ALSO
    Task.

